com.ptc.windchill.wp

Class WorkPackageEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • wt.events.KeyedEvent
      • com.ptc.windchill.wp.WorkPackageEvent

  • public class WorkPackageEvent
extends KeyedEvent
    Used to represent events occurring within the WorkPackage services. This event supports multiple object event targets.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
